snippet.title: That Blooming Feeling - Trailer
snippet.description:
A game by the Tot's Team! 

Welcome to That Blooming Feeling, a Gardening Videopicturebook about welcoming a youthful joy into our selves. 

Pass the time with a sweet water drop as you roll about, goof around, and watch your friends grow up.

Available at: https://totsteam.itch.io/thatbloomingfeeling
